    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e8eacda01606cb55e857ab42e1cced72.poster.avif?t=1728632541\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e8eacda01606cb55e857ab42e1cced72.webm?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e8eacda01606cb55e857ab42e1cced72.mp4?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add Last Viking to your wishlist!</h2><br>Meet Ragnar the Glorious, a Viking who overslept Ragnarok after a bit too much mead. Now, he must embark on a quest to gather the shattered pieces of the broken world, locate Odin and Thor, and steer time back on its fated course.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/ecbd606fc972e9d4f4a80aa45c6f5695.poster.avif?t=1728632541\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/ecbd606fc972e9d4f4a80aa45c6f5695.webm?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/ecbd606fc972e9d4f4a80aa45c6f5695.mp4?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Assisted by the Valkyrie, our Viking sets sail on raids along the colossal serpent Jormungandr's spine. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e39d38662c045a5789cc76b982d40ec8.poster.avif?t=1728632541\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e39d38662c045a5789cc76b982d40ec8.webm?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/e39d38662c045a5789cc76b982d40ec8.mp4?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>There, he battles a variety of mythical creatures from Scandinavian lore, builds lands, and gathers experience and resources to restore Valhalla.<br><br>But he can only achieve this with your help! <br>Strap on your helmet, grab your battle-ax, and get ready for a wild running on the back of a giant serpent! The fate of the world rests on your shoulders (or, more accurately, on the serpent's back).<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/3fd159839d0ceab8607cbd4b8519f9c9.poster.avif?t=1728632541\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/3fd159839d0ceab8607cbd4b8519f9c9.webm?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074820/extras/3fd159839d0ceab8607cbd4b8519f9c9.mp4?t=1728632541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>• Humorous storyline with adorable cat characters <br>• Battles against mythical foes <br>• Deckbuilding<br>• Epic boss encounters <br>• Merge lands and weapons <br>• Various heroes to manage and upgrade<br>• Loops on the Serpent's back and loops of great gameplay",
